d get","should have got","must get","should getting"],"correct":1,"explanation":"O'tmishda kutilgan, lekin ehtimol sodir bo'lmagan narsa haqida 'should have + V3' ishlatiladi."},{"id":"u35","unit":35,"section":"Modals","unitTitle":"I'd better … it's time …","prompt":"It's 11 o'clock. It's time ___ home.","options":["we go","we went","we will go","we going"],"correct":1,"explanation":"'It's time' dan keyin fe'l Past Simple shaklida keladi, garchi ma'no hozirgi/kelajakka tegishli bo'lsa ham: It's time we went."},{"id":"u36","unit":36,"section":"Modals","unitTitle":"would","prompt":"If I had a lot of money, I ___ travel around the world.","options":["will","would","can","must"],"correct":1,"explanation":"Xayoliy (real bo'lmagan) shart gapning natija qismida 'would' ishlatiladi."},{"id":"u37","unit":37,"section":"Modals","unitTitle":"can/could/would you …? (requests, offers)","prompt":"___ you pass me the salt, please?","options":["Do","Are","Could","Must"],"correct":2,"explanation":"Iltimos qilishning odobli shakli — 'Could you …?' — 'Do you' dan ko'ra ancha xushmuomalaroq so'roq shakli."},{"id":"u38","unit":38,"section":"if and wish","unitTitle":"if I do … and if I did …","prompt":"What would you do if you ___ a lot of money?","options":["win","won","will win","would win"],"correct":1,"explanation":"Xayoliy/kam ehtimolli hozirgi-kelajak shart uchun 'if + Past Simple, ... would' qolipi ishlatiladi: if you won."},{"id":"u39","unit":39,"section":"if and wish","unitTitle":"if I knew … I wish I knew …","prompt":"I wish I ___ how to fix this problem, but I have no idea.","options":["know","knew","have known","will know"],"correct":1,"explanation":"Hozirgi holatdan norozilik/istak bildirishda 'wish + Past Simple' ishlatiladi: I wish I knew (lekin bilmayman)."},{"id":"u40","unit":40,"section":"if and wish","unitTitle":"if I had known … I wish I had known …","prompt":"If I ___ you were ill, I would have visited you.","options":["knew","had known","have known","know"],"correct":1,"explanation":"O'tmishdagi real bo'lmagan shart (uchinchi tur shart gap) uchun 'if + Past Perfect, ... would have + V3' ishlatiladi."},{"id":"u41","unit":41,"section":"if and wish","unitTitle":"wish","prompt":"It's raining again. I wish it ___ raining.","options":["stops","stopped","would stop","stop"],"correct":2,"explanation":"Boshqa birov/vaziyat o'zgarishini istaganda 'wish + would' ishlatiladi — his-hayajon/noroziliqni bildiradi: I wish it would stop."},{"id":"u42","unit":42,"section":"Passive","unitTitle":"Passive 1 (is done / was done)","prompt":"Many accidents ___ by careless driving.","options":["cause","are caused","caused","causing"],"correct":1,"explanation":"Ish kim tomonidan bajarilishi muhim bo'lmasa, majhul nisbat (be + V3) ishlatiladi: are caused by."},{"id":"u43","unit":43,"section":"Passive","unitTitle":"Passive 2 (be done / been done / being done)","prompt":"My car ___ at the moment, so I came by bus.","options":["is repairing","is being repaired","has repaired","repairs"],"correct":1,"explanation":"Hozir davom etayotgan jarayonning majhul shakli 'is/are being + V3' bo'ladi: is being repaired."},{"id":"u44","unit":44,"section":"Passive","unitTitle":"Passive 3","prompt":"I was surprised that I ___ to the interview.","options":["wasn't invited","didn't invite","wasn't inviting","hadn't invited"],"correct":0,"explanation":"Bu yerda gap egasi (I) harakatni bajarmayapti, unga nisbatan bajarilmoqda — shuning uchun majhul shakl: wasn't invited."},{"id":"u45","unit":45,"section":"Passive","unitTitle":"it is said that … he is said to … he is supposed to …","prompt":"He is supposed ___ a lot of money, but he lives quite simply.","options":["to have","having","have","to having"],"correct":0,"explanation":"'be supposed to' dan keyin infinitiv keladi; o'tmishga tegishli bo'lsa 'to have + V3' shaklida: is supposed to have."},{"id":"u46","unit":46,"section":"Passive","unitTitle":"have something done","prompt":"I don't cut my own hair. I ___ cut by a hairdresser.","options":["have it","have","am having","have it done"],"correct":3,"explanation":"Boshqa birov siz uchun biror ishni bajarganda 'have something done' qolipi ishlatiladi: have it cut/have it done."},{"id":"u47","unit":47,"section":"Reported speech","unitTitle":"Reported speech 1 (he said that …)","prompt":"Direct speech: Paul said, 'I am feeling ill.' Reported speech: Paul said that he ___ feeling ill.","options":["is","was","has been","will be"],"correct":1,"explanation":"Ko'chirma gapda asosiy fe'l o'tgan zamonda bo'lsa (said), 'am/is' — 'was'ga o'zgaradi."},{"id":"u48","unit":48,"section":"Reported speech","unitTitle":"Reported speech 2","prompt":"Direct: 'I'll call you tomorrow,' she said. Reported: She said (that) she ___ me the next day.","options":["will call","would call","calls","was calling"],"correct":1,"explanation":"Ko'chirma gapga o'tganda 'will' — 'would'ga o'zgaradi, va 'tomorrow' — 'the next day' bo'ladi."},{"id":"u49","unit":49,"section":"Questions and auxiliary verbs","unitTitle":"Questions 1","prompt":"Who ___ the window? (asking who did it)","options":["did break","broke","did broke","was broken"],"correct":1,"explanation":"'Who' savol egasi bo'lganda, so'roq so'zidan keyin 'do/did' qo'shilmaydi, fe'l to'g'ridan-to'g'ri keladi: Who broke the window?"},{"id":"u50","unit":50,"section":"Questions and auxiliary verbs","unitTitle":"Questions 2 (do you know where …?)","prompt":"Do you know what time ___?","options":["does the film start","the film starts","is the film starting","start the film"],"correct":1,"explanation":"Ichki (yashirin) savolda so'z tartibi to'g'ridan-to'g'ri gapdagidek bo'ladi (do/does yordamchisi qo'shilmaydi): what time the film starts."},{"id":"u51","unit":51,"section":"Questions and auxiliary verbs","unitTitle":"Auxiliary verbs / I think so, I hope so","prompt":"'Are you tired?' 'I don't ___ .'","options":["think so","think it","think that","not think"],"correct":0,"explanation":"Qisqa javob berishda 'I think so / I hope so / I don't think so' kabi qisqartma qoliplar ishlatiladi."},{"id":"u52","unit":52,"section":"Questions and auxiliary verbs","unitTitle":"Question tags (do you? isn't it?)","prompt":"You haven't seen this film, ___?","options":["have you","haven't you","did you","didn't you"],"correct":0,"explanation":"Bosh gap salbiy (haven't) bo'lsa, tag-savol ijobiy bo'ladi: haven't seen ... have you?"},{"id":"u53","unit":53,"section":"-ing and to …","unitTitle":"Verb + -ing (enjoy doing / stop doing)","prompt":"I enjoy ___ to music while I'm working.","options":["listen","to listen","listening","listened"],"correct":2,"explanation":"'Enjoy' fe'lidan keyin gerundiy (-ing) shakli keladi: enjoy listening."},{"id":"u54","unit":54,"section":"-ing and to …","unitTitle":"Verb + to … (decide to / forget to)","prompt":"It was late, so we decided ___ a taxi home.","options":["taking","take","to take","took"],"correct":2,"explanation":"'Decide' fe'lidan keyin infinitiv (to + fe'l) keladi: decided to take."},{"id":"u55","unit":55,"section":"-ing and to …","unitTitle":"Verb (+ object) + to … (I want you to …)","prompt":"I didn't want anybody ___ what had happened.","options":["knowing","know","to know","knew"],"correct":2,"explanation":"'Want somebody to do something' qolipi: fe'l + shaxs + to + infinitiv: want anybody to know."},{"id":"u56","unit":56,"section":"-ing and to …","unitTitle":"Verb + -ing or to … 1 (remember, regret)","prompt":"I remember ___ this photo — it was a beautiful day.","options":["to take","taking","take","took"],"correct":1,"explanation":"'Remember doing' — o'tmishda sodir bo'lgan va eslab qolgan harakat: remember taking (rasmni olganimni eslayman)."},{"id":"u57","unit":57,"section":"-ing and to …","unitTitle":"Verb + -ing or to … 2 (try, need, help)","prompt":"The room was cold, so I tried ___ the heating on.","options":["turning","to turn","turn","turned"],"correct":1,"explanation":"'Try to do' — biror qiyin ishga harakat qilish ma'nosida: tried to turn (isitgichn